      AVBMC_ATOM        1
      AVBMC_RMAX        5.0
      AVBMC_RMIN        1.0
      PBIAS        0.5
    &END AVBMC
    &MAX_DISPLACEMENTS
      &BOX_DISPLACEMENTS
        RMVOLUME        100.5
      &END BOX_DISPLACEMENTS
      &MOL_DISPLACEMENTS
